#

Grilled Herb and Honey Glazed Pork

25 min
$12.99
220 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreePaleo

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

GrilledQuickEasyPorkDinner

Description

Juicy pork tenderloin glazed with a sweet herb-infused honey sauce, perfect for a quick weeknight dinner.

Ingredients

  • pork tenderloin: 1 lb
  • honey: 1/4 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • fresh rosemary: 1 tbsp, chopped
  • fresh thyme: 1 tbsp, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • salt: 1 tsp
  • black pepper: 1/2 tsp
